            "config": {
              "id": "QUE59244",
              "question": "Sean has an interview for a job at a company in London. Although he did not go to a “public” school, he did get an excellent education at a free school and attended university at Oxford. His resume is good and his references are excellent, but when he arrives at the interview, the interviewer immediately pegs Sean as working class and no longer seems interested in hiring him. How did the interviewer know what class Sean came from?\n\u003cbr /\u003e",
